@bohurupi_santiniketan 
Is presenting new collections on Men's vintage Panjabi wear.
The culmination of these designs are inspired by Satyajit Ray's simple yet royal look in his films.

Bengali cinema has been a great part of all of our childhood memories especially when it comes to Satyajit Ray. He has inspired the entire entertainment industry to think something out of the box, each of his creations are a masterpiece of itself. 
Bohurupi Santiniketan and @jalsaghar_calcutta took this 'Ray-emotion' through a creative path, which will help all of us to understand how Ray's imagination kept on inspiring us.
This entire design of apparel is a tribute to his journey.

The journey of 𝐁𝐨𝐡𝐮𝐫𝐮𝐩𝐢 𝐒𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐤𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐧 takes a bold new turn as we step into the future as 𝐑o𝐲 𝐂𝐚𝐥𝐜𝐮𝐭𝐭𝐚. This transformation embodies our commitment to preserving heritage while embracing modern sophistication.

A new identity. The same passion for excellence. Get ready to experience a brand that seamlessly blends tradition with innovation.

Something big is coming—stay tuned.

✨ 𝐀𝐧 𝐄𝐯𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐢𝐧 𝐄𝐱𝐜𝐞𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 ✨

We are proud to announce the next step in our journey. 𝐁𝐨𝐡𝐮𝐫𝐮𝐩𝐢 𝐒𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐤𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐧 will now be known as 𝐑o𝐲 𝐂𝐚𝐥𝐜𝐮𝐭𝐭𝐚—a name that reflects our deep connection to tradition while paving the way for a bold and innovative future.

This transformation is more than just a change in name; it’s a redefinition of our vision, combining heritage with contemporary elegance to offer you an unparalleled experience.

Stay with us as we unveil this exciting new chapter.

#roycalcutta #bohurupisantiniketan #newchapter #rebranding #traditionmeetsmodern #elegance #innovation #commitment #10years #newjourney #unveilingsoon #excitingtimes #heritage #luxury #experience #calcutta #newbeginnings #watchthisspace #staytuned #comingsoon

✨ 𝐀 𝐍𝐞𝐰 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐧𝐬 ✨
Big things are on the horizon for us! After 10 years of celebrating timeless traditions under the name 𝐁𝐨𝐡𝐮𝐫𝐮𝐩𝐢 𝐒𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐤𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐧, we’re evolving with a bold new identity: 𝐑o𝐲 𝐂𝐚𝐥𝐜𝐮𝐭𝐭𝐚.

This change marks the start of something extraordinary, staying true to our roots while embracing the future of fashion and heritage. Stay tuned for the unveiling of a legacy redefined.
